Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:30.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sledeći put na Melanholiji Suzumije Haruhi:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:31.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Epizoda devet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:31.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Greška.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:33.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Utuvi više to u glavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:34.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sledeći put na Melanholiji Suzumije Haruhi:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:35.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Epizoda šest...
